  learningGoals: [`Locate the three major ethical lenses (deontology, utilitarianism, virtue ethics) inside familiar sci-fi dilemmas.`, `See how rigid rule systems interact, conflict, and fail under real-world pressure.`, `Recognize the way metrics, feedback loops, and predictive systems can harden human fallacies into infrastructure.`],
